_sText:
Gun game map up to 42 players, composed of one main room, 2 spawns and 2 corridors. 

To install this map, just extract the zip file in "SteamApps\common\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike".

**Note :** Cubemaps seems to be broken in CSS. If anyone got a fix, just contact me.

**Edit :** Fixed T spawns.
